## Proposed Changes

### Phase 1: Cart & Shipping (Admin + Storefront)

#### [NEW] [page.jsx](file:///c:/Users/User/Downloads/antigravity/ecommerce-platform/app/admin/orders/shipping/page.jsx)
- New admin page at `/admin/orders/shipping` for managing shipping costs
- Admin sets **per-item shipping cost** (quantity-based: cost × quantity)
- Stored in Firestore at `clients/{clientId}/settings/shipping`
- Fields: `perItemCost` (number), `enabled` (boolean)

#### [MODIFY] [layout.jsx](file:///c:/Users/User/Downloads/antigravity/ecommerce-platform/app/admin/layout.jsx)
- Add "Shipping" link under Orders section in admin nav

#### [MODIFY] [page.jsx](file:///c:/Users/User/Downloads/antigravity/ecommerce-platform/app/(storefront)/cart/page.jsx)
- Remove `city` input field and `BD_CITIES` import
- Remove free shipping logic (`freeThreshold`, `shipping === 0` checks)
- Fetch shipping cost from Firestore settings (per-item × total quantity)
- Remove `city` from order data

#### [MODIFY] [storage.js](file:///c:/Users/User/Downloads/antigravity/ecommerce-platform/lib/storage.js)
- Add `getSettings(clientId, key)` and `saveSettings(clientId, key, data)` methods for shipping/discount/logo configs

