### Phase 2: Product Detail Page Cleanup

#### [MODIFY] [page.jsx](file:///c:/Users/User/Downloads/antigravity/ecommerce-platform/app/(storefront)/products/[id]/page.jsx)
- **Remove fake discount**: Delete countdown timer, fake 20% inflation, cookie-based timer logic
- **Show real discount**: Only display discount when `product.salePrice` exists and is less than `basePrice`
- **Hide reviews section**: Remove `<ReviewsSection>` component render
- **Hide "Delivery and return policies" & "Did you know?"**: Remove from `<AccordionSections>` — only keep "Item details"
- **Show ALL related products**: Remove `.slice(0, 6)` — show all filtered products with horizontal scroll or grid
- **Fix nav/wishlist button icons**: Use consistent `ChevronLeft`/`ChevronRight` icons, add white bg with shadow for visibility on dark images
- **Fix image gallery height**: Implement Alibaba-style gallery — thumbnails get fixed height matching main image, with up/down scroll buttons (no visible scrollbar)
- **Make wishlist functional**: Integrate with localStorage-based wishlist state, toggle save/unsave
- **Mobile-first responsive**: Rework grid to be mobile-first (single column → desktop 2-col)

#### [MODIFY] [ProductDetailSections.jsx](file:///c:/Users/User/Downloads/antigravity/ecommerce-platform/components/storefront/ProductDetailSections.jsx)
- Remove "Delivery and return policies" accordion section
- Remove "Did you know?" accordion section
- Remove `ReviewsSection` export (hide from storefront)

#### [MODIFY] [page.jsx](file:///c:/Users/User/Downloads/antigravity/ecommerce-platform/app/admin/products/[id]/edit/page.jsx)
- Remove entire Reviews Management section (hide from admin)

