## Verification Plan

### Automated Tests
- `npm run build` — verify no build errors after all changes
- Browser testing of all affected pages:
  - `/cart` — verify no city field, shipping from admin
  - `/products/[id]` — verify no fake discount, no reviews, no timer, proper gallery
  - `/products` — verify no search input, proper loading state
  - `/wishlist` — verify new page works
  - `/login`, `/signup` — verify new pages work
  - `/account`, `/account/orders` — verify theme consistency
  - `/admin/orders/shipping` — verify shipping config
  - `/admin/homepage` — verify logo settings
  - Navbar search — verify it navigates to products with query

### Manual Verification  
- Test on mobile viewport (375px width) for all pages
- Verify wishlist save/remove across product details and "you may also like"
- Verify shipping cost calculation in cart (per-item × quantity)
